<div class="legal-page">
  <h1 class="legal-title">Customer Care</h1>
  <div class="legal-body">
<p class="cc-intro">Everything you might want to know before, during, and after your order. If your question isn't here, we're a short message away at Hello@cieristudio.com.</p>
<h2>Frequently Asked</h2>
<p class="cc-q">What size should I order?</p><p>Our pieces are designed with a relaxed, considered fit. For your closest match, refer to the size chart below. Each product page also lists the height and size worn by the model in our editorial imagery, which can be a helpful reference.</p>
<p class="cc-q">How do I track my order?</p><p>When your order is dispatched, you'll receive an email from Hello@cieristudio.com with your tracking number and link. Tracking is usually live within 24-48 hours of that email.</p>
<p class="cc-q">When will my order ship?</p><p>In-stock orders are dispatched within 1-3 business days. You'll receive a confirmation email with tracking once your order is on its way. Pre-order and made-to-order pieces ship on the date listed on the product page.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Do you ship internationally?</p><p>Yes, we ship worldwide. Shipping rates are calculated at checkout. See Shipping &amp; Delivery below for delivery times by region.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Do I have to purchase in USD?</p><p>No. Choose your currency at the top right of the screen - you can shop in USD, CAD, AUD, GBP and EUR.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Can I return or exchange an item?</p><p>Returns are accepted within 14 days of delivery, provided pieces are unworn, unwashed, and have their original tags attached. Returns are refunded as store credit, which never expires. We don't offer direct exchanges - simply return your piece for credit and place a new order. Return shipping is arranged and paid by you. Discounted items and gift cards are final sale. Full details are under Returns below.</p>
<p class="cc-q">What if my order arrives damaged or faulty?</p><p>While we do our best to ensure this never happens, if you receive a damaged piece or a manufacturing fault occurs, contact us immediately at Hello@cieristudio.com and we'll do our best to resolve it. After 45 days from receiving the product, any damage is considered wear and tear rather than a manufacturing fault.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Received something you didn't order?</p><p>If you received a product different from the one you ordered, contact us at Hello@cieristudio.com and we'll get you the pieces you ordered.</p>
<p class="cc-q">How do I care for my CIERI pieces?</p><p>Our pieces are made to be lived in, which means cared for gently. As a general rule: machine wash cold with like colours, and lay flat out of direct sunlight to dry. See the full care guide below, or the label sewn into each garment.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Can I cancel or change my order?</p><p>Once an order is placed, we're unable to make changes or cancellations, as pieces are prepared for dispatch quickly. Please review your size, shipping address, and order details carefully before completing checkout. If something is wrong, reach us as soon as possible and we'll help where we can.</p>
<p class="cc-q">What if the product I want is sold out?</p><p>Subscribe on the product page to be notified when the item is restocked.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Have a question we haven't answered?</p><p>Don't hesitate to reach out to us or email at Hello@cieristudio.com for any additional questions and concerns.</p>
