<p class="cc-q">Care</p>
<ul><li>Machine wash in cold water with like colours.</li><li>Lay garments separately flat out of direct sunlight to dry.</li><li>Ensure garments are completely dry prior to storing.</li><li>Avoid contact with rough surfaces, as it can cause fabric pulling.</li><li>Take care with perfumes, deodorants, body lotions and makeup, and allow them to dry fully before dressing.</li></ul>
<h2>Shipping &amp; Delivery</h2>
<p>We ship worldwide. Once your order is on its way, you'll receive a confirmation email with tracking.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Processing time</p><p>Orders are processed within 1-3 business days. During sale periods and holidays, processing may take a little longer.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Shipping rates &amp; delivery</p><p>Shipping rates are calculated at checkout based on your destination. Estimated delivery times after dispatch:</p>
<ul><li>Southeast Asia (Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, the Philippines): 5-7 business days</li><li>Europe, the UK, North America, and Australia: 10-15 business days</li></ul>
<p>Delivery estimates are not guaranteed, as transit can be affected by customs and the carrier.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Duties &amp; taxes</p><p>International orders may be subject to import duties and taxes set by your country. These are not included at checkout and are the responsibility of the customer, usually collected by the carrier on delivery.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Lost, stolen, or delayed packages</p><p>Once your order is handed to the carrier, CIERI cannot take responsibility for parcels that are lost, stolen, delayed, or delivered to an incorrect address entered at checkout. If your parcel is missing, check with neighbours, building reception, and safe spots near your door, then contact us and we'll do our best to help.</p>
<h2>Returns</h2>
<p>We want every CIERI piece to feel right. If it doesn't, eligible items can be returned within 14 days of delivery for store credit.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Our returns policy</p><p>You have 14 days from the date your order is delivered to request a return. To be eligible, items must be returned in their original condition:</p>
<ul><li>New, unworn, unwashed, and undamaged</li><li>Free of odours, stains, makeup, deodorant, and pet hair</li><li>With all original tags, hygiene stickers, and packaging attached and intact</li></ul>
<p>We inspect every return and reserve the right to decline any item that does not meet these requirements. Sale and discounted items, and gift cards, are final sale and cannot be returned.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Store credit</p><p>All approved returns are refunded as store credit, issued for the full value of the returned item. Store credit does not expire and can be used on any future order. We do not offer refunds to the original payment method.</p>
<p class="cc-q">How to start a return</p><p>Email us at Hello@cieristudio.com with your order number and the item(s) you would like to return. We'll confirm your return and share the return address. Please wait for our confirmation before sending anything back, as items returned without prior authorisation cannot be accepted.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Return shipping</p><p>Return shipping is arranged and paid by the customer. We recommend a tracked service, as we cannot take responsibility for returns lost in transit. Original shipping charges are non-refundable. For international returns, any customs duties or taxes incurred are the customer's responsibility. Items from different orders must be returned separately, each under its own return confirmation.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Exchanges</p><p>We do not offer direct exchanges. To change a size or colour, return your item for store credit and place a new order for the piece you would like.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Changes &amp; cancellations</p><p>Once an order is placed we begin processing it right away and cannot make changes or cancellations. Please review your size, items, and address carefully before checking out.</p>
<p class="cc-q">Fair use of returns</p><p>Our return policy is offered in good faith. We reserve the right to limit or decline returns, or to restrict future orders, for accounts that show a pattern of excessive returns of non-faulty items.</p>
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>For anything we haven't answered here, write to us. We respond within one business day, often sooner.</p>
<p><strong>Hello@cieristudio.com</strong><br>Monday to Friday, 09:00-17:00 AEST</p>
